race.comment: SWAG (1) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in four of six career outings and strikes a very winnable contest here. Gets the services of Maloney to navigate from the sticky draw and will be at peak fitness now third-up from the break. Rates the testing material. WAYBURN (4) went down by the narrowest of margins on debut and Mallyon stays in the saddle following that first-up placing. Can open the winning account this time. ENFORCEABLE (3) resumes here but showed ability in his first preparation and has revved up for this with a recent trial placing. Top-three credentials while fresh. MR DEMOCRAT (5) strips fitter second-up from the break and may make his presence felt.
